    "Secondly, we conducted a thorough examination of data sources.",
    "Our analysis covered both public and private datasets used in these studies.",
    "Noted that some review articles lacked detail on dataset content, we focused on providing comprehensive information on public datasets, including their origins and sample sizes.",
